title: Ep. - 193 - UNSOLVED MYSTERY CASES AND REAL HOUSEWIVES REVIEW
description:
Colin Gooch’s fiancé makes him watch a prodigious amount of reality shows. He graciously reviews this week’s wild episode of Real Housewives of Orange County. 


Medium Nicole Michelle discusses with Kate the TLC series Taken at Birth, and several unsolved cases including the disappearance of Kristin Smart, the murder of Missy Bevers, and whether Kevin Cooper is guilty of the crimes he’s been convicted. 



Reality Life with Kate Casey
